bilingual.source: It's a social online city building sim .

手边保持一个词典，最好是在线的。

bilingual.source: Yes, online news and information is a big reason.
bilingual.target: 是的，在线的新闻和信息是一大原因。

bilingual.source: In each parts, it use local and online operating ways.
bilingual.target: 每个功能模块都可由现场的或在线的两种操作方式实现。

bilingual.source: Sure, mapping your offline social network online is fun.
bilingual.target: 确实，描绘一下自己的离线社交网站在线的情况很有趣。

bilingual.source: Also includes an Online JPG to SWF converter with preloader.
bilingual.target: 也包括了一个预载的在线的JPG到SWF的转换器。

bilingual.source: This is the website of American Physiological Society Journals Online.
bilingual.target: 这是美国生理学会期刊在线的网站。

bilingual.source: According to Nielsen Online, social networks and blogs are now the 4th most popular kinds of online activities.
bilingual.target: 根据尼尔森在线的数据，网络社交（social network）和博客目前已经成为第四种最流行的线上活动。

list.abstract: online，英 [ˌɒnˈlaɪn]，美 [ˌɑːnˈlaɪn]。英文单词，网络用语。形容词为受电脑控制的，联机的。副词为联机地，在电脑操控下。通常加在游戏名称末尾时表示网络游戏。短语为get online（上网）。例句为：“I can search useful information online.”（我可以在网上搜索有用的信息）。 反义词为off-line。

yingyinNormal.en: Got it. Seen it. Detailed analysis posted online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有了。看过了。我的详细分析已经发到网上了。

yingyinNormal.en: These giant wind farms are quickly coming online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些硕大的风电场即将迅速投用。

yingyinNormal.en: He can direct Chicago work our way. Checked online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他可以让我们在芝加哥顺风顺水，网上查的。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, have you read the online reviews for this place?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看过网上对这地方的评价吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Good morning, Dolores. Bring yourself back online. Hello.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早上好，德洛丽丝，立即上线。你好。

yingyinNormal.en: Then we'd better move. The system goes online at midnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们得赶快行动，系统将在午夜上线。

yingyinNormal.en: We are going to play the online game. The online game?! Bully!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们准备玩网游。网游？！更妙！

yingyinNormal.en: The x-tens are online.
yingyinNormal.zh: X-10(先进网络技术)已经联网了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hummus. I read online that chickpeas are high in natural estrogen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鹰嘴豆泥，网上说鹰嘴豆含有大量雌激素。

yingyinNormal.en: You guys get started. What are you doing? Going online to buy shoes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家开工。你在干嘛？上网买鞋子。

yingyinNormal.en: And please take down the online video of your client playing our song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有请你们把网上你们委托人的表演视频撤下。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that's easy. Anyone can go online and get ordained as a minister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那简单，谁都可以上网受任当证婚牧师。

yingyinNormal.en: He's not my teacher anymore. I now attend a prestigious online academy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他已经不是我的老师了，我现在开始在网上听课了。

yingyinNormal.en: We're a family of fire starters, poison eaters, and online prostitutes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们这家子有玩火的，有吃毒药的，还有上网卖淫的。

yingyinNormal.en: Bring yourself back online, Maeve. Do you know why you're here? I'm afraid not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 立即上线，梅芙，知道你为什么会在这里吗？我不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait! I know. I'm going to conduct an interview with myself and post it online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道啦，做个自访，然后放到网上去。

yingyinNormal.en: I've seen that. Yeah. Serial Apeist. Howard found it online the day we met you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看过哎，叫"连环杀人猩"嘛。见到你的第一天，Howard就上网找到了。

yingyinNormal.en: Why not? With online shopping and overnight delivery, I can get anything I want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么不能？有网上购物和隔天送达，我要什么有什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, he is an astronaut. And he didn't start an online petition to get Wil fired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的确是个宇航员啊。他也没有发动炒威尔鱿鱼的网上情愿。

yingyinNormal.en: No. It's getting a lot of traction online. Should be all over the news by morning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，网上已经有很多关注了。到早上应该报道满天飞了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Suppose you are organizing an <highlight>online</highlight> meeting.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假设你正在组织一个线上会议。

examination_example.sentence: Rules would prevent broadband providers from picking winners and losers <highlight>online</highlight>, preserving the freedom and innovation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 规则将阻止宽带提供商在网上挑选赢家和输家，阻止保持自由和创新。

examination_example.sentence: Rules need to be set to diversify <highlight>online</highlight> services.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 需要为多样化在线服务设置规则。

examination_example.sentence: However, they are sometimes unable to recognize false information on the Internet, judge the reliability of <highlight>online</highlight> information sources.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，他们有时无法识别互联网上的虚假信息，无法判断在线信息来源的可靠性。

examination_example.sentence: One should think twice upon reading <highlight>online</highlight> comments and information, as they may be groundless and fictitious just to catch people's attention.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个人在阅读网上的评论和信息时应该三思，因为它们可能是毫无根据和虚构的，只是为了引起人们的注意。

examination_example.sentence: You may buy gifts for someone, but they track each item, and if your gift ends up <highlight>online</highlight> they know who to ask.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你可能会给某人买礼物，但他们会跟踪每一件物品，如果你的礼物最终出现在网上，他们知道该问谁。

word_usage.usage:
online作形容词，表“在线的, 联机的”，也可作副词，表“在线”。
示例：(1) Online shopping is very cheap.
网上购物很便宜。
(2) He booked a seat online.
他在线预订了一个座位。
